law.text: Controlled insurers and controlling producers which are not in compliance with KRS 304.3-410 on July 14, 1992, shall have sixty (60) days after July 14, 1992, to comply, and shall comply with KRS 304.3-415 beginning with all policies written or renewed on or after sixty (60) days after July 14, 1992.
law.history: Created 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 6, effective July 14, 1992.
